OL,3,CKemi Badenoch says 'lower council tax'
OL,4,Cpledge didn't mean people would pay
OL,5,Cless
OL,7,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch is asked by
OL,8,FITV News Meridian's Kit Bradshaw about
OL,9,FConservative campaign pledges at last
OL,10,Fyear's local elections
OL,12,FA Conservative campaign pledge to
OL,13,F'lower council tax' didn't mean people
OL,14,Fwould actually pay less tax, Kemi
OL,15,FBadenoch has claimed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
