OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774361471
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch says 'lower council tax'
OL,4,Cpledge didn't mean people would pay
OL,5,Cless
OL,7,FThe Tory leader was asked to explain
OL,8,Fwhy county councils controlled by her
OL,9,Fparty were putting council tax up,
OL,10,Fdespite the party's local election
OL,11,Fslogan last year promising to deliver
OL,12,F'lower taxes, better services'.
OL,14,FKemi Badenoch told ITV News Meridian:
OL,15,F"Compared to other parties, we do have
OL,16,Flower taxes. Council tax goes up with
OL,17,Finflation. Sometimes it's dependent on
OL,18,Fthe funding that they get from
OL,19,Fnational government."
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
