PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774361471
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch says 'lower council tax'
OL,4,Cpledge didn't mean people would pay
OL,5,Cless
OL,7,FConservative-run county councils in
OL,8,FEast Sussex and West Sussex are
OL,9,Fincreasing council tax by the maximum
OL,10,Fof 4.99% for 2026/27. Reform UK-run
OL,11,FKent County Council is increasing
OL,12,Fcouncil tax by 3.99%.
OL,14,FAsked about why the Tories were
OL,15,Fincreasing bills to a greater degree
OL,16,Fthan Reform UK in the South East, Ms
OL,17,FBadenoch said: "There are many other
OL,18,FConservative councils that have lower
OL,19,Fincreases. People have to do what is
OL,20,Fright for their local areas.
OL,26,@yD@POU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774361471
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch says 'lower council tax'
OL,4,Cpledge didn't mean people would pay
OL,5,Cless
OL,7,F"Sussex might have more social care
OL,8,Fduties that it needs to provide. It
OL,9,Fall depends on local areas. But what
OL,10,FI'm saying is that in every single
OL,11,Farea, the Conservatives will give you
OL,12,Fthe best deal.
OL,14,F"My councillors are thinking about
OL,15,F(the cost of living) every single day.
OL,16,FThey're not wasting money hiring more
OL,17,Fadvisers like (Reform are) doing in
OL,18,FKent."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUwD@ApmwD@TpnyD@OpmyD@ZpnzD@
OL,26,AFO]
