OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774361471
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch says 'lower council tax'
OL,4,Cpledge didn't mean people would pay
OL,5,Cless
OL,7,FIn response to the interview, a Reform
OL,8,FUK spokesman said: "Kemi's
OL,9,FConservatives left a trail of chaos
OL,10,Fand financial mismanagement in their
OL,11,Fwake. In Kent, the Reform
OL,12,Fadministration inherited over #700
OL,13,Fmillion of debt from her party."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
