FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774361471
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch says 'lower council tax'
OL,4,Cpledge didn't mean people would pay
OL,5,Cless
OL,7,FThe spokesperson added: "We're now
OL,8,Fcleaning up their mess, making and
OL,9,Fidentifying over #700 million of
OL,10,Fsavings in our first year and
OL,11,Fachieving the lowest average council
OL,12,Ftax position of any political party.
OL,13,FIn Kent alone, we've delivered the
OL,14,Flowest tax rise in a decade without
OL,15,Fany cuts to frontline services."
OL,17,FEarlier this month, Nigel Farage
OL,18,Fdefended his county councillors in
OL,19,FKent hiking bills despite election
OL,20,Fliterature promising to 'reduce waste
OL,21,Fand cut your taxes'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
