PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774361471
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch says 'lower council tax'
OL,4,Cpledge didn't mean people would pay
OL,5,Cless
OL,7,FThe Reform UK leader told ITV News
OL,8,FMeridian: "Well, cutting taxes could
OL,9,Fmean not putting them up as much, I
OL,10,Fsuppose. But I never promised cuts in
OL,11,Fcouncil tax."
OL,13,FKemi Badenoch was speaking on a
OL,14,Fcampaign visit to East Grinstead in
OL,15,FWest Sussex. Local elections are due
OL,16,Fto take place across large parts of
OL,17,Fthe South and South East on Thursday,
OL,18,F7 May.
OL,26,@pD@KOUsD@MO]
